summary: hey small thing about killing eve I super appreciated?  villanelle was frequently described as 'slim', but she still did not...
body: hey small thing about killing eve I super appreciated? villanelle was frequently described as ‘slim’, but she still did not look underweight. she had hips, and her jaw wasn’t always razor sharp, and sometimes her stomach stuck out a bit, and when she was in fitted clothes and she sat down you could see the rolls (because Everyone’s stomach has rolls when you sit it’s literally just what having skin entails). and her arms weren’t twigs because she was physically strong and trained for hand-to-hand combat so why would they be. and she was still flexible enough to get into a suitcase. AND she ate like a regular human, on screen, never with anyone commenting on her eating. no more presentation of underweight women and crying “this is sexy!!”. villanelle is terrifying and intriguing and sexy as hell and all the while she has the physical build of a normal human person and wow the bar is low but I appreciate it nonetheless.
